snippet.title: House Flipper - HGTV DLC release date!
snippet.description:
The time has come to tell you when you'll be able to play HTGV DLC! 

Join us on the Official House Flipper Discord and become a member of our amazing community!

- Stay updated about House Flipper's development,
- Chat, ask questions and share your houses with other players,
- Hang out with developers!

Link: https://discord.gg/houseflipper

Social media channels:
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/HouseFlipperOfficial/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HouseFlipperGame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/houseflippersim
Twitch.tv: https://www.twitch.tv/frozen_district
